      </row>
      <row>
        <id>35</id>
        <qid>236</qid>
        <question>Which banking, currency, sanctions, transfer, or documentation constraints affect receiving funds? Select all that apply.</question>
        <help>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help:&lt;/strong&gt; Receiving money can be blocked by banking, transfer, documentation, de-risking, or safety issues. Select all that apply and use unsafe/not sure if needed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; Use the safest accurate answer. If exact details create risk, use an approximate answer or choose Not applicable / Unsafe to answer.&lt;/p&gt;</help>
        <script />
        <language>en</language>
      </row>
