      <row>
        <id>96</id>
        <qid>5080</qid>
        <question>Other</question>
        <help />
        <script />
        <language>en</language>
      </row>
      <row>
        <id>97</id>
        <qid>240</qid>
        <question>How is the organisation led by, accountable to, or connected with the communities it serves? Select all that apply.</question>
        <help>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help:&lt;/strong&gt; Funders often look for proof that the work is grounded in community reality, not only designed for a proposal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; Select the ways community voice, leadership, feedback, request, participation or accountability currently shapes the work.&lt;/p&gt;</help>
        <script />
        <language>en</language>
      </row>
      <row>
        <id>99</id>
        <qid>242</qid>
        <question>What is the approximate current team size?</question>
        <help>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help:&lt;/strong&gt; Team size affects delivery capacity, reporting load, and grant-size fit. Include paid staff, regular consultants, volunteers, and movement labour honestly.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; Use the safest accurate answer. If exact details create risk, use an approximate answer or choose Not applicable / Unsafe to answer.&lt;/p&gt;</help>
        <script />
        <language>en</language>
      </row>
      <row>
        <id>100</id>
        <qid>243</qid>
        <question>Which governance or oversight structures are currently active? Select all that apply.</question>
        <help>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversight can look different across CSOs. Select all structures that currently provide accountability, decision review, or governance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; Use the safest accurate answer. If exact details create risk, use an approximate answer or choose Not applicable / Unsafe to answer.&lt;/p&gt;</help>
        <script />
        <language>en</language>
      </row>
      <row>
        <id>101</id>
        <qid>5081</qid>
        <question>Formal board</question>
        <help />
        <script />
