        <surveyls_language>en</surveyls_language>
        <surveyls_title>DOO U Grant Funding Conversion Diagnostic — Report-Aligned 24-Driver Assessment</surveyls_title>
        <surveyls_description>&lt;p&gt;A premium, shame-free diagnostic for identifying why strong applications may not convert into conversations, due diligence, awards or renewal — and what should be repaired, verified, protected or routed differently before the next ask.&lt;/p&gt;</surveyls_description>
        <surveyls_welcometext>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Welcome.&lt;/strong&gt; This diagnostic is aligned to the DOO U Grant Funding Conversion Report. It reads your answers across 12 result areas and 24 funding conversion drivers: context, legal route, market intelligence, pipeline discipline, fit, competitiveness, access, relationships, trust, proposal quality, governance, operations and financial health.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please answer from current reality, not aspiration. Choosing “not sure”, “not applicable” or “unsafe to answer” is allowed where a question requires verification or protection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Estimated time:&lt;/strong&gt; 45–70 minutes. Best completed by someone who understands programmes, finance/admin, fundraising and leadership realities.&lt;/p&gt;</surveyls_welcometext>
        <surveyls_endtext>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thank you.&lt;/strong&gt; Your responses have been saved. The diagnostic report will use your answers to identify result bands, repair priorities, document and evidence readiness, route recommendations, protected evidence handling and practical 30/60/90 next steps.&lt;/p&gt;</surveyls_endtext>
        <surveyls_policy_notice />
        <surveyls_policy_notice_label />
        <surveyls_url />
        <surveyls_urldescription />
      </row>
    </rows>
